#. Tag: title
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid "plasmoidviewer User's Manual"
msgstr "Manual d'usuari del plasmoidviewer"

#. Tag: date
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "2017-01-09"
msgstr "9 de gener de 2017"

#. Tag: releaseinfo
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plasma 5.8"
msgstr "Plasma 5.8"

#. Tag: productname
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "KDE Plasma"
msgstr "Plasma del KDE"

#. Tag: manvolnum
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"
msgstr "<manvolnum>1</manvolnum>"

#. Tag: refpurpose
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "Run Plasma widgets in their own window"
msgstr "Executa els ginys del Plasma a la seva pròpia finestra"

#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>plasmoidviewer</command> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-v, --"
"version</option></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-c, --containment</"
"option> <replaceable>name</replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt"
"\"><option>-a, --applet</option> <replaceable>name</replaceable></group> "
"<group choice=\"opt\"><option>-f, --formfactor</option> <replaceable>name</"
"replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-l, --location</option> "
"<replaceable>name</replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-x, --"
"xPosition</option> <replaceable>xPosition</replaceable></group> <group "
"choice=\"opt\"><option>-y, --yPosition</option> <replaceable>yPosition</"
"replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-s, --size</option> "
"<replaceable>widthXheight</replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt"
"\"><option>-p, --pixmapcache</option> <replaceable>size</replaceable></"
"group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-t, --theme</option> <replaceable>name</"
"replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-h, --help</option></"
"group> <arg choice=\"opt\">args</arg>"
msgstr ""
"<command>plasmoidviewer</command> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-v, --"
"versió</option></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-c, --containment</"
"option> <replaceable>nom</replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt"
"\"><option>-a, --applet</option> <replaceable>nom</replaceable></group> "
"<group choice=\"opt\"><option>-f, --formfactor</option> <replaceable>nom</"
"replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-l, --location</option> "
"<replaceable>nom</replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-x, --"
"xPosition</option> <replaceable>posicióX</replaceable></group> <group choice="
"\"opt\"><option>-y, --yPosition</option> <replaceable>posicióY</"
"replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-s, --size</option> "
"<replaceable>ampladaXalçada</replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt"
"\"><option>-p, --pixmapcache</option> <replaceable>mida</replaceable></"
"group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-t, --theme</option> <replaceable>nom</"
"replaceable></group> <group choice=\"opt\"><option>-h, --help</option></"
"group> <arg choice=\"opt\">args</arg>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descripció"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>plasmoidviewer</command> is a graphical tool allowing developers to "
"test Plasma applets."
msgstr ""
"<command>plasmoidviewer</command> és una eina gràfica que permet als "
"desenvolupadors provar les miniaplicacions Plasma."

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only installed applets will be found. <command>kbuildsycoca5</command> may "
"need to be run for newly-installed applets to be found."
msgstr ""
"Només s'hi troben les miniaplicacions instal·lades. <command>kbuildsycoca5</"
"command> pot necessitar ser executat per a trobar les miniaplicacions de "
"nova instal·lació."

#. Tag: title
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opcions"

#. Tag: option
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v, --version"
msgstr "-v, --version"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays version information."
msgstr "Mostra informació de la versió."

#. Tag: option
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "-c, --containment <replaceable>name</replaceable>"
msgstr "-c, --containment <replaceable>nom</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the containment plugin."
msgstr "El nom del connector contenidor."

#. Tag: option
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "-a, --applet <replaceable>name</replaceable>"
msgstr "-a, --applet <replaceable>nom</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the applet plugin."
msgstr "El nom del connector miniaplicació."

#. Tag: option
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "-f, --formfactor <replaceable>name</replaceable>"
msgstr "-f, --formfactor <replaceable>nom</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The formfactor to use (horizontal, vertical, mediacenter, planar or "
"application)."
msgstr ""
"El factor de format a utilitzar (horitzontal, vertical, centre multimèdia, "
"planar o aplicació)."

#. Tag: option
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "-l, --location <replaceable>name</replaceable>"
msgstr "-l, --location <replaceable>nom</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location constraint to start the Containment with (floating, desktop, "
"fullscreen, topedge, bottomedge, leftedge, rightedge)."
msgstr ""
"La restricció de la ubicació amb la qual s'ha d'iniciar el contenidor "
"(flotant, escriptori, pantalla completa, vora superior, vora inferior, vora "
"esquerra, vora dreta)."

#. Tag: option
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "-x, --xPosition <replaceable>xPosition</replaceable>"
msgstr "-x, --xPosition <replaceable>posicióX</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the x position of the plasmoidviewer on the Plasma desktop."
msgstr ""
"Ajusta la posició «x» del visualitzador de plasmoides a l'escriptori de "
"Plasma."

#. Tag: option
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "-y, --yPosition <replaceable>yPosition</replaceable>"
msgstr "-y, --yPosition <replaceable>posicióY</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the y position of the plasmoidviewer on the Plasma desktop."
msgstr ""
"Ajusta la posició «y» del visualitzador de plasmoides a l'escriptori de "
"Plasma."

#. Tag: option
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "-s, --size <replaceable>widthXheight</replaceable>"
msgstr "-s, --size <replaceable>ampladaXalçada</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the window size of the plasmoidview."
msgstr "Ajusta la mida de la finestra del visualitzador de plasmoides."

#. Tag: option
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "-p, --pixmapcache <replaceable>size</replaceable>"
msgstr "-p, --pixmapcache <replaceable>mida</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "The size in KB to set the pixmap cache to."
msgstr "La mida en kB per a fixar la memòria cau del mapa de píxels."

#. Tag: option
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid "-t, --theme <replaceable>name</replaceable>"
msgstr "-t, --theme <replaceable>nom</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the theme which the shell will use."
msgstr "El nom del tema amb el qual s'emprarà des de l'intèrpret d'ordres."

#. Tag: option
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "-h, --help"
msgstr "-h, --help"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays this help."
msgstr "Mostra aquesta ajuda."

#. Tag: replaceable
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "args"
msgstr "args"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data that should be passed to the applet as 'externalData' event."
msgstr ""
"Les dades que s'han de passar a la miniaplicació com a esdeveniment «dades "
"externes»."

#. Tag: title
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "See Also"
msgstr "Vegeu també"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More detailed user documentation is available from <ulink url=\"help:/plasma-"
"desktop\">help:/plasma-desktop</ulink> (either enter this <acronym>URL</"
"acronym> into &konqueror;, or run <userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> "
"<parameter>help:/plasma-desktop</parameter></userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Hi ha informació més detallada disponible en <ulink url=\"help:/plasma-"
"desktop\">help:/plasma-desktop</ulink> (podeu emprar aquest &URL; al "
"&konqueror; o bé executar <userinput><command>khelpcenter</command> "
"<parameter>help:/plasma-desktop</parameter></userinput>)."

#. Tag: title
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "Authors"
msgstr "Autors"

#. Tag: para
#: man-plasmoidviewer.1.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>plasmoidviewer</command> was written by "
"<personname><firstname>Aaron</firstname><surname>Seigo</surname></"
"personname> <email>aseigo@kde.org</email>."
msgstr ""
"<command>plasmoidviewer</command> ha estat escrit per en "
"<personname><firstname>Aaron</firstname><surname>Seigo</surname></"
"personname> <email>aseigo@kde.org</email>."
